        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your dive and water sports gear fresh and long-lasting with the GEAR AID Wetsuit Shampoo and BCD Cleaner Deluxe Kit. This concentrated, unscented formula cleans and conditions neoprene wetsuits, drysuits, booties, and life jackets, effectively removing salt, chlorine, and residue that can break down materials and cause odor over time. Ideal for bin soaking, the Revivex Wetsuit and Drysuit Shampoo helps restore and protect your scuba equipment after every use. The liquid cleaner is safe for rubber surfaces and formulated with natural ingredients, making it a reliable choice for maintaining your gear. Each deluxe kit contains a 30 mL bottle designed to keep your neoprene and scuba equipment clean, conditioned, and ready for your next adventure.",
